00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:39,360
Yes, that's correct.
是的，没错。

158
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:42,000
She filled me in on the details of the job on the telephone.
她在电话里向我详细介绍了这份工作的细节。

159
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,000
Great.
很好。

